{"tid":520624,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]South Park: Phone destroyer 於11月9日係球上線","createTime":"2018-01-05T15:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T11:47:30.000Z","uid":100391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a062b653e1935c38bf3691421c8c0b0f3ed68209","tid":520624,"uid":100391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.images.southparkstudios.com/blogs/southparkstudios.com/files/2017/06/sp-phone-destroyer-blog.jpg?quality=0.8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.images.southparkstudios.com%2Fblogs%2Fsouthparkstudios.com%2Ffiles%2F2017%2F06%2Fsp-phone-destroyer-blog.jpg%3Fquality%3D0.8&h=93711cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://southparkphonedestroyer.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsouthparkphonedestroyer.com%2F&d=47bLBQiuShvRDyQFUVKHy5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8e55d2bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://southparkphonedestroyer.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n          由 Ubisoft 旗下 RedLynx 工作室與《南方四賤客》電視動畫原創作者 Trey Parker 及 Matt Stone 合作開發的《南方四賤客：電話破壞狂》，是一款結合了即時戰鬥與傳統的集換式卡片機制的手機遊戲，目前已於 Google Play 展開預先註冊，預估上線日期為 2017 年 11 月 9 日。<br />\n<br />\n　　《南方四賤客：電話破壞狂（South Park: Phone Destroyer）》將於 11 月 9 日在全球正式發佈，玩家如果現在參加預先註冊，就能在遊戲推出時取得可裝扮虛擬人偶的獨家「人熊豬」造型。<br />\n<br />\n　　官方表示，《南方四賤客：電話破壞狂》融合了經典的南方四賤客人物、緊張刺激的即時戰略、玩家對戰、原汁原味的南方四賤客幽默和卡牌收集要素，集結西部牛仔、巫師、改造人等等眾多勢力，組成終極隊伍，準備好打趴對手。<br />\n<br />\n　　遊戲中將包含經典角色另類新版本，例如「遠古屎蛋」、「改造人阿尼」、「客家忍者凱子」、「巫師王阿ㄆ一ㄚˇ」，還有其他更多角色，並且與 South Park Digital Studios 合作編劇，帶領玩家體驗無厘頭的單人遊戲劇情。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/3/154633.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F3%2F154633.html&d=47bLBQiuShvRDyQFUVKHy5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d4242fe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/3/154633.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－－－－<br />\n仲有冇人玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係好好玩但好呃錢<br />\n唔比錢基本上去到中途係玩唔落去<br />\n打咩都打唔贏 又冇錢又冇卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0f53596439b2e8dda60e58c560abd27e366ac7","tid":520624,"uid":49285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"淨係有玩The Fractured But Whole"},{"pid":"69f8b691fe85c55867d6fb120c20decccfb845cf","tid":520624,"uid":14606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"D卡好難升 晤畀錢又冇靚卡"},{"pid":"49e3fa3eae63128d9c2995233492f5baab905626","tid":520624,"uid":100391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0f53596439b2e8dda60e58c560abd27e366ac7","tid":520624,"uid":49285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"淨係有玩The Fractured But Whole"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:27:37.000Z","msg":"想玩但係exchange緊得mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前玩過The Stick of Truth 好撚正"},{"pid":"81a2792bce667b7c732a342a60f30f442393f724","tid":520624,"uid":100391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69f8b691fe85c55867d6fb120c20decccfb845cf","tid":520624,"uid":14606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"D卡好難升 晤畀錢又冇靚卡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:33:02.000Z","msg":"抽多幾次都抽到既 但升唔到都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加6lv pvp13 pvp開始打唔過啲人 單人又刷到關關都打唔過<br />\n刷到去第5，6次啲怪3，4lv開始頂唔順<br />\n搞到完全冇素材又冇錢又冇pvp卷又開唔到pvp卡包<br />\n玩唔撚到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496574dd6f109c9fc749b30507e3e633f128e580","tid":520624,"uid":104106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a062b653e1935c38bf3691421c8c0b0f3ed68209","tid":520624,"uid":100391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.images.southparkstudio